TITLE: Creating Associated Entities in Shopware 6
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to create a tax entity at the same time as creating a product. Instead of providing a taxId, the code provides the full tax entity data in the tax field, which causes a new tax entity to be created and associated with the product.
