LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
public function writeData(Context $context): void
{
    $this->productRepository->create([
        [
            'name' => 'Example product',
            'productNumber' => 'SW123',
            'stock' => 10,
            'tax' => ['name' => 'test', 'taxRate' => 15],
            'price' => [['currencyId' => Defaults::CURRENCY, 'gross' => 50, 'net' => 25, 'linked' => false]],
        ]
    ], $context);
}
```

