TITLE: Disabling Indexing in Shopware DAL Update Method
DESCRIPTION: This PHP code snippet shows how to disable indexing when using the Data Abstraction Layer (DAL) in a Shopware indexer update method. It adds a flag to the context to prevent infinite loops caused by EntityWrittenContainerEvent events.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shopware/docs/blob/main/guides/plugins/plugins/framework/data-handling/add-data-indexer.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: PHP
CODE:
```
public function update(EntityWrittenContainerEvent $event): ?EntityIndexingMessage
{
    $updates = $event->getPrimaryKeys(CustomerDefinition::ENTITY_NAME);

    if (empty($updates)) {
        return null;
    }

    $context = $event->getContext();
    $context->addState(EntityIndexerRegistry::DISABLE_INDEXING);

    return new EntityIndexingMessage(array_values($updates), null, $context);
}
```

