TITLE: HTTP Media Download Service Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of HttpMediaDownloadService that handles downloading media files from source system via HTTP. Includes support checking and processing logic with parallel download capabilities.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shopware/docs/blob/main/products/extensions/migration-assistant/concept/media-processing.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: php
