TITLE: Decorating Service Method
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to decorate a service method to add additional functionality or modify its behavior.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shopware/docs/blob/main/guides/plugins/plugins/administration/services-utilities/add-custom-service.md#2025-04-22_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
Shopware.Application.addServiceProviderDecorator('joker', joker => {
    const decoratedMethod = joker.joke;

    joker.joke = function () {
        return decoratedMethod.call(joker).then(joke => ({
            ...joke,
            funny: joke.id % 2 === 0
        }))
    };

    return joker;
});
```

