TITLE: Implementing a B2B API Route Provider in PHP
DESCRIPTION: This PHP class `MyApiRouteProvider` implements the `RouteProvider` interface to define custom API routes for the B2B Suite. The `getRoutes` method returns an array of route definitions, each specifying the HTTP method, the sub-route path (relative to `/api/b2b`), the DIC service ID of the controller, and the action method name.
