TITLE: Implementing Feature Flag for Conditional Association Autoloading in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Example code showing how to conditionally add an association field to a field collection based on the v6.6.0.0 feature flag. This allows for backward compatibility during the transition from autoloaded associations to explicit loading.
