TITLE: Defining Special Field Types in Shopware 6 Entities
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to use special field types like AutoIncrement and ForeignKey in Shopware 6 entities. These fields implement specific behaviors and have their own PHP attribute classes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shopware/docs/blob/main/guides/plugins/plugins/framework/data-handling/entities-via-attributes.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

