TITLE: Implementing Custom Storefront Controller in Shopware PHP
DESCRIPTION: Example controller implementation that creates a route '/example' accessible via frontend.example.example. Extends StorefrontController and includes basic route configuration for storefront scope.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shopware/docs/blob/main/guides/plugins/plugins/content/seo/add-custom-seo-url.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

